Requirements: Android OS 1.5 +
Overview: The Best Manga Reader for Android

Read your favorite manga on your phone. You can read online or download and read later. You can open your manga from sdcard (png, jpg, zip). Share in Facebook and Twitter. Read manga fromhttp://www.mangareader.net and etc. Read the manga in English, French, Russian, Spanish, German and Arabic.
Have multitouch and one finger zoom!

